    +DOMElement
      h3 Meteor-TLV ReCharge
      h2 Famous-Views
      img.gravatar(src='/img/gravatar.png')
      h3 13th June, 2015
      p These slides are available at:
        br
        a(href="http://meetup-fview-tlv.meteor.com/") gadi.cc/meteor-tlv
